== 音韻差異 ==

在河內腔中，後面3組的字母並沒有發音上的差別：<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">tr</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">ch</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">{{IPA|[tɕ]}}</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">d</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">r</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">gi</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">[z]</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">s</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">x</span>=<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">{{IPA|[s]}}</span>。但是在西貢腔中，<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">r</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">s</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">tr</span>需要捲舌，<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">ch</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">gi</span>、<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">x</span> 沒有捲舌。而且西貢腔將 <span lang="vi" dir="ltr">d</span> 唸做半元音{{IPA|[j]}}。

